name: ⭕️ MLNDR Founders Collection: 002/Aaron
description: Aaron. A role model father and husband that will do anything to provide his family against all odds.  Set in a dystopian future where natural resources are scarce and pollution is a global problem, the MLNDR Family Series will portray how I see our future as a species if our hunger for non-renewable natural resources continues to grow at the current pace.   The Founders collection will be comprised of 6 characters who will play as leading actors in my MLNDR Family series.   Holders of this token participate for a chance to win one of 10 NFTs from my props collection.
